{"tid":1471313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日反思點樣改進，明天繼續上路","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:51:42.000Z","uid":55974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"690d1c893a89bc4388d540be7b88dd7235a955ad","tid":1471313,"uid":55974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"今日比人入埋，跟哂對家個故仔，收埋花，攞哂彩。但係唔緊要，大家目標仲係五大訴求，一日未死，一日運動都繼續。<br />\n<br />\n好多人怕民意逆轉，係嫁，係會有嫁。所以快d同身邊既人講翻，用盡諗到既方法去做。錯係錯左，我地唔同政府，我地肯認錯，肯改善。我地做既行為唔係為左係鏡頭講句野去收割道德高地，只要香港可以係去翻一個公平，公正既社會，我地願意走上街頭，係我地褲袋攞出僅有既錢去支援運動，甚至犧牲自己前途，承擔法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n因為我地係香港人，係愛呢個地方既香港人。"},{"pid":"a803088e3cb1657c14a2c422d143592750d4538c","tid":1471313,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb1cec614440bbb1d890056421853e3801d2d245","tid":1471313,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:41:28.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有好提議"},{"pid":"5401e7ad4bbdcd4128ef20e7fc82bf2a9e5be97e","tid":1471313,"uid":55974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"818 上街"},{"pid":"a4a01d9c95c3b381ba45c87b9ba53a71c418e8f3","tid":1471313,"uid":57018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"文宣諗下點將對面拉幫拉派，呢個就係敵人最叻，我地做得最少！<br />\n<br />\n例如張建宗講過警察唔好既，煲大講！<br />\n警察內部四分五裂既，煲大講！<br />\n警察前線同上頭不滿既，煲大講！<br />\n民建聯同何生唔岩傾，煲大講！<br />\n民建聯同梁芬元秋唔岩傾，煲大講！<br />\n<br />\n煲畀對面啲人聽，記住宣傳唔係對內，係對外！"},{"pid":"4ea8303bf5f9560aa8f761a5f9b70009d8f91da6","tid":1471313,"uid":55974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"818 上街"},{"pid":"8027da9bc5d63e5972fe7e4ccea9561efa6df153","tid":1471313,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:51:42.000Z","msg":"其實今日仲有深水埗燒衣<br />\n唔只要討論，仲要加強文宣<br />\n<br />\n我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}